creator: Solar A/S
descriptionHtml: With Solar Mobile you will easily find what you need to buy. The improved filtering options make it easier to find the right products. Add your favourite service center in the app and pick up your order locally - or get it delivered as a Fastbox. If you don't have the time to complete your order right away, you may save it as a draft and open it later - either through the app or from the web shop. If you happened to get the wrong product you can quickly create a return order using the app.
